data_table.description: Subject ID, study center, case or control, gender, age groups, and population structure principal component of participants with or without renal cell carcinoma and involved in the "National Cancer Institute (NCI) Genome-Wide Association Study (GWAS) of Renal Cell Carcinoma in African Americans" project.

variable.name: AFFECTION_STATUS
variable.description: Case or control status of the subject

variable.name: AGE_GROUP
variable.value: Greater or equal to 75 years old

variable.name: EV4
variable.description: Population structure principle component (ie., eigenvalue) that is significantly associated with AFFECTION_STATUS
